      {
        "id": "FR-001",
        "description": "重写analyze()端点函数：\n1. 接收AnalyzeRequest请求体（Pydantic自动校验）\n2. 调用_build_agent_instances()构建3个Agent实例\n3. 调用run_workflow(request, agent_instances)执行工作流\n4. 将run_workflow返回的dict转换为AnalyzeResponse\n5. 返回AnalyzeResponse（设置response_model_by_alias=True以输出camelCase）\n6. 异常时返回统一错误格式{code, message, data, timestamp}",
        "priority": "P0",
        "acceptance_condition": "POST /api/agent/analyze返回AnalyzeResponse格式，字段完整"
      },
      {
        "id": "FR-002",
        "description": "实现_build_agent_instances()辅助函数：\n1. 从app_state获取llm_service/search_service/prompt_manager/reranker\n2. 构建RetrieverAgent(name='retriever', llm_service=..., search_service=..., reranker=..., prompt_manager=...)\n3. 构建AnalyzerAgent(name='analyzer', llm_service=..., prompt_manager=...)\n4. 构建GeneratorAgent(name='generator', llm_service=..., prompt_manager=...)\n5. 返回{'retriever': retriever, 'analyzer': analyzer, 'generator': generator}字典\n6. 如果app_state中某服务未初始化，抛出ModelNotLoadedException",
        "priority": "P0",
        "acceptance_condition": "3个Agent实例正确构建，依赖服务从app_state注入"
      },
      {
        "id": "FR-003",
        "description": "run_workflow返回结果到AnalyzeResponse的映射：\n- analysis_id ← result['analysis_id']\n- status ← result.get('status', 'completed')\n- report ← result.get('report')\n- citations ← result.get('citations', [])\n- agent_states ← 将result['agent_states']字典转为List[AgentStateResponse]\n- degraded ← result.get('degraded', False)\n- degraded_reason ← result.get('degraded_reason')",
        "priority": "P0",
        "acceptance_condition": "响应字段映射正确，camelCase输出格式正确"
      },
      {
        "id": "FR-004",
        "description": "AgentStateResponse转换逻辑：\n将agent_states字典中的每个Agent状态转为AgentStateResponse：\n- agent_name ← key\n- status ← value['status']\n- progress ← value.get('progress')\n- intermediate_result ← value.get('intermediate_result')\n- duration_ms ← value.get('duration_ms')",
        "priority": "P0",
        "acceptance_condition": "agent_states列表格式正确，每个元素符合AgentStateResponse"
      },
      {
